{"tid":1485282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"牆外留學生就可以集會, 而牆內中國人只可以帝吧出征","createTime":"2019-08-18T15:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T01:10:22.000Z","uid":125079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f849eacbcaaf78919f03d3fea878f357bbaf3a61","tid":1485282,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:46:36.000Z","msg":"中國人係中國冇集會支持香港警察同反港獨<br />\n<br />\n淨係開埋啲帝吧出征, 咩鬼飯圈女孩<br />\n<br />\n但一覺得要企出黎親身支持, 個個潛曬水扮睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n啲外國留學生, 就鬼死咁勇猛咁日日亂叫亂打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後牆內中國人拍手叫好, 完全冇諗過自己都可以咁做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C9MMU1v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC9MMU1v.png&h=2a4f6a57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aEG88mD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaEG88mD.png&h=34de6c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/18/233649_de8086c737d1d96837fb8479c0bb5c1e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F18%2F233649_de8086c737d1d96837fb8479c0bb5c1e.png&h=a754e94d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有日日係度死撐死黑警, 屈示威者<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NJ6EvB5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNJ6EvB5.png&h=bfc64c34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ziaaChq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FziaaChq.png&h=497c6220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/18/234533_44d49ba9227082d2a2b16827e0be4a81.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F18%2F234533_44d49ba9227082d2a2b16827e0be4a81.png&h=ccf74d92&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40f1878e05fd371abec76f5dd1cfcf7eb6131eb6","tid":1485282,"uid":125079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:57:04.000Z","msg":"大家多啲到 Twitter IG Reddit 留言出post<br />\n<br />\n肯離開同溫層未啊。。。。。。成個twitter都係五毛大軍洗版。。。香港人除左自己圍內打飛機之外仲識咩。。。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1479651\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1479651</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"acdd60d9686dd2a326806c22e574dfbefa6a9918","tid":1485282,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:58:38.000Z","msg":"佢地真係仲死撐緊香港黑警<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/18/235809_04f718f1434969c0dbf5bba0f3fff7f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F18%2F235809_04f718f1434969c0dbf5bba0f3fff7f7.png&h=e0cd5e67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c540b9f010a2d156fa3cef2cd918ab97be06d50","tid":1485282,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁中國人唔公平<br />\n<br />\n啲留學生就可以出黎載歌載舞"},{"pid":"2ab13ea9f3fd2077028760f949c64c3a01c8fe82","tid":1485282,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:13:05.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以幫中國人集下會 反港獨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4a7d5ac3cde021f9f0f576c778681d8ce4a573","tid":1485282,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:13:43.000Z","msg":"中國人好慘 但留學生集得會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015b86be15af32c752ffa7e387531a912c035247","tid":1485282,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=